1296.name: L-Ag2P
1296.Applications:
Particularly recommended for sanitary, refrigerating and large tubing installations..Do not use in a sulphurous environment. 
For working temperatures up to 200ºC
1296.Suitable_For: Phosphorus silver brazing alloy. Self picking on copper. Copper to copper (without flux). Brass, copper and copper-tin alloys (with flux).
